<li><a href="https://noyb.eu/en/preliminary-noyb-win-meta-stops-ai-plans-eu">(Preliminary) noyb WIN&#160;: Meta stops AI plans in the EU</a> (noyb.eu)<br />
<blockquote><p>In reaction to 11 noyb complaints, the DPC has announced (late Friday afternoon) that Meta has pledged to the DPC that it will not process EU/EEA user data for undefined “artificial intelligence techniques”. Previously Meta argued it had a “legitimate interest” in doing so, only informing (some) users about the change and merely allowing a (deceptive and complicated) “opt-out”.</p></blockquote>
